{"tid":637200,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【回帶】李 澤 楷 持 有 中 興 首 曝 光","createTime":"2018-04-21T14:42:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-22T08:14:55.000Z","uid":5195,"like":51,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"f187087b3e8c625e46a600803a86dc33e8952c7c","tid":637200,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T14:42:39.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】電訊盈科（008）主席李澤楷增持中興通訊（763）股份，達需申報水平。據港交所股權披露顯示，李澤楷於上月27日，透過旗下私募基金PineBridge，場內增持中興通訊好倉50.32萬股，其持股量由4.94%增至5%，現持股量達3,780.8萬股。<br />\n<br />\n上月增持股份至5%<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，李澤楷以每股平均價17.562元增持股份，持股量增至5%，涉資883.7萬元，該股上周五收市報17.26元，較其增持均價低逾1.7%，李澤楷持有股份市值逾6.64億元。<br />\n由於之前李澤楷持股量不足半成毋須申報，故今次是其持有中興股份消息首次「浮面」。<br />\n據資料顯示，目前李澤楷直接持有超過5%股權的港股有電盈、香港電訊（6823）及盈大地產（432），僅餘的600股東亞銀行（023）股份已在10月中全數沽出。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20151206/19401249\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20151206%2F19401249&d=NCDN%2BRr8j1hfn9LkkYcFGEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=3eebd35d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20151206%2F19401249&h=1ef42bc0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20151206/19401249</a><br />\n<br />\n有Richard拓住個價有乜好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"547355e7a8efe1d93bed19081062a2eebe9d6570","tid":637200,"uid":83582,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T14:44:35.000Z","msg":"6億對於佢黎講係小數目"},{"pid":"62c76357d8c0faaa2075b63029457bd9caccee7b","tid":637200,"uid":124450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T14:45:31.000Z","msg":"走得好 走得鬼馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c42f22cc55e7b69add491198bcc20bb20d81d569","tid":637200,"uid":37735,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T15:33:13.000Z","msg":"能力好不如命好<br />\n<